title: 08/19/2021 DPS Best of
itunes:title: 08/19/2021 DPS Best of
description:
Jonas Knox, Brady Quinn and LaVar Arrington, in for DP, debate whether or not this will be Aaron Rodgers "farewell tour" in Green Bay. LaVar is bullish on Zach Wilson having the best rookie season out of this QB draft class. The guys call Tom Brady a liar for denying he's miffed with the Titans picking Ryan Tannehill over him last offseason and they read into the high praise for Jalen Hurts so far this preseason.
